{
  "stem": "9558.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had a feeling [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that he's not going to live through the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's what he said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in case she should come out alive-- so he wants somebody should take care of her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were married in the ghetto, in April the 6th, 1943.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And then we were together until, in the ghetto, until September, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] before they sent us to Szebnie.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And then when they separated us in Auschwitz, she was together with my sisters.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And she told me they all died on typhus.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At the same time?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was there an epidemic?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] We made up-- if you'll come out alive, we should meet in Bochnia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they separated us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came-- I was liberated by Schindler.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before we do that, let's talk a little bit more about Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In those first three weeks, when you were together with your brothers and Mayer, and your friend, were you given work?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you have work to do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to carry stones, about two or three kilometers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I must have been young and strong, because a lot of people died doing that job.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They gave us big stones to carry one way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the other people carried the same stones back, like a torture.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For no reason at all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With the German Shepherds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if you, God forbid if you dropped the stone-- if you didn't hold it, if you didn't carry it, the German Shepherds ate you up alive.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was a horrible three weeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then when they sent us away, already-- Buna, it wasn't-- comparing what it was, it was much better there.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
